[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 5.0,
    "text": "Okay, let me see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.0,
    "endTime": 7.0,
    "text": "Okay, I got it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.0,
    "endTime": 11.0,
    "text": "Hey, I know you hate being ugly, but somebody has to make everyone else look good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.0,
    "endTime": 17.0,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.0,
    "endTime": 21.0,
    "text": "Oh, yes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.0,
    "endTime": 24.0,
    "text": "Yes, yes, yes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.0,
    "endTime": 25.0,
    "text": "Mm-hmm!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.0,
    "endTime": 30.0,
    "text": "Oh, sweetheart, you have got it going on!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 32.0,
    "text": "Oh, you are high-stylin', babe!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.0,
    "endTime": 37.0,
    "text": "Those c'mere sailor eyes, that kiss-and-tell coat..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.0,
    "endTime": 37.0,
    "text": "Hey, Pearl!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.0,
    "endTime": 42.0,
    "text": "That is my sister you got your mitts all over!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.0,
    "endTime": 44.0,
    "text": "And if you know what is good for you, you..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.0,
    "endTime": 49.0,
    "text": "Come now, my little meadow muffin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.0,
    "endTime": 52.0,
    "text": "My studio is just over here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.0,
    "endTime": 52.0,
    "text": "Ooh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.0,
    "endTime": 56.0,
    "text": "Oh, you know it, baby!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.0,
    "endTime": 58.0,
    "text": "Ooh, let me have it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.0,
    "endTime": 58.0,
    "text": "Let me have it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.0,
    "endTime": 64.0,
    "text": "Oh, isn't it wonderful, big brother?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.0,
    "endTime": 68.0,
    "text": "I am going to be a model."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.0,
    "endTime": 72.0,
    "text": "And you even let me keep the beauty mark."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.0,
    "endTime": 73.0,
    "text": "Really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.0,
    "endTime": 80.0,
    "text": "That was probably just some weirdo who likes to take pictures of big, fat, ugly..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.0,
    "endTime": 80.0,
    "text": "Nah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.0,
    "endTime": 85.0,
    "text": "Come on, this is all stuck."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.0,
    "endTime": 87.0,
    "text": "What would you do without me, Cal?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.0,
    "endTime": 90.0,
    "text": "You would be no ways."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.0,
    "endTime": 91.0,
    "text": "Oh, I guess so."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.0,
    "endTime": 100.0,
    "text": "Just what clown in his right mind is going to make a fashion model out of a tooth-torn slab of cheese like you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.0,
    "endTime": 101.0,
    "text": "You're probably right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.0,
    "endTime": 104.0,
    "text": "Of course I am!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.0,
    "endTime": 108.0,
    "text": "Just what do you see when you look at one of these beauty mags anyway?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 108.0,
    "text": "Me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 109.0,
    "text": "Sure it's you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.0,
    "endTime": 116.0,
    "text": "You don't think they would just put any old cow..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.0,
    "endTime": 116.0,
    "text": "It can't be!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.0,
    "endTime": 122.0,
    "text": "Oh, what a glorious cow!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.0,
    "endTime": 123.0,
    "text": "Okay, okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.0,
    "endTime": 125.0,
    "text": "No shoving, please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.0,
    "endTime": 141.0,
    "text": "Dear diary, you ain't never gonna believe what I am about to write down on yours."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.0,
    "endTime": 141.0,
    "text": "Any questions?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.0,
    "endTime": 143.0,
    "text": "Um, yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.0,
    "endTime": 149.0,
    "text": "May I be excused to go adjust my other strap?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.0,
    "endTime": 150.0,
    "text": "Well, by all means!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.0,
    "endTime": 156.0,
    "text": "Class is dismissed early today so we can all adjust our other straps!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.0,
    "endTime": 158.0,
    "text": "Hi, Cal!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.0,
    "endTime": 167.0,
    "text": "I never liked you before, but now that you're famous, I like you a lot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.0,
    "endTime": 170.0,
    "text": "Oh, jeez, it's just my stupid sister already."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.0,
    "endTime": 175.0,
    "text": "Oh, that cow baloney is so last Tuesday."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.0,
    "endTime": 175.0,
    "text": "No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.0,
    "endTime": 175.0,
    "text": "Moses!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.0,
    "endTime": 176.0,
    "text": "Oh, no!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.0,
    "endTime": 191.0,
    "text": "I'm not famous anymore!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.0,
    "endTime": 196.0,
    "text": "So, you got a little taste of the spotlight, huh, cow?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.0,
    "endTime": 199.0,
    "text": "And you'd like to get back there again, hmm?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.0,
    "endTime": 201.0,
    "text": "Welcome to my milk bar!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.0,
    "endTime": 203.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.0,
    "endTime": 203.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.0,
    "endTime": 207.0,
    "text": "Ten cents a glass."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.0,
    "endTime": 217.0,
    "text": "Isn't that a pretty penny?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.0,
    "endTime": 219.0,
    "text": "It's ten cents a glass."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.0,
    "endTime": 223.0,
    "text": "I have to fill so many."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.0,
    "endTime": 229.0,
    "text": "I would like to go home now, Mr. Bartender."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.0,
    "endTime": 230.0,
    "text": "Home?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.0,
    "endTime": 232.0,
    "text": "Don't you understand, cow?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.0,
    "endTime": 236.0,
    "text": "You work for me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.0,
    "endTime": 240.0,
    "text": "This seedy milk bar is your home!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.0,
    "endTime": 240.0,
    "text": "Now sing!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.0,
    "endTime": 244.0,
    "text": "We'll be getting some customers in here soon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.0,
    "endTime": 247.0,
    "text": "And they'll expect a show with milk!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.0,
    "endTime": 249.0,
    "text": "Ten cents a glass."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.0,
    "endTime": 253.0,
    "text": "Isn't that a pretty penny?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.0,
    "endTime": 258.0,
    "text": "I wonder what happened to my large sister."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.0,
    "endTime": 259.0,
    "text": "Hey, that sounds like..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.0,
    "endTime": 262.0,
    "text": "Ooh, a customer!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.0,
    "endTime": 265.0,
    "text": "What'll it be, pal?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.0,
    "endTime": 268.0,
    "text": "Hey, hey, that you, sis?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.0,
    "endTime": 271.0,
    "text": "Oh, don't look at me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.0,
    "endTime": 274.0,
    "text": "Hey, hey, it's okay, sis."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.0,
    "endTime": 277.0,
    "text": "Come on, come on, let's get you out of here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.0,
    "endTime": 278.0,
    "text": "There, there, little fella."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.0,
    "endTime": 283.0,
    "text": "Don't get your waddle in a knot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.0,
    "endTime": 287.0,
    "text": "How about I fix you up a nice ice cream cone?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.0,
    "endTime": 293.0,
    "text": "Ooh, this tastes like it has a bug in it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.0,
    "endTime": 295.0,
    "text": "Well, I don't see no bug, chicken."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.0,
    "endTime": 297.0,
    "text": "Well, look a little closer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.0,
    "endTime": 298.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.0,
    "endTime": 299.0,
    "text": " Ah!"
  }
]